text modes
0 - 8x8 characters, 40 columns, 25 rows*
1 - 4x8 characters, 80 columns, 25 rows*
2 - 8x8 stretched characters, effective 16x8, 20 columns, 25 rows*
3 - 8x8 stretched characters, effective 8x16, 40 columns, 12 rows*
4 - 8x8 stretched characters, effective 16x16, 20 columns, 12 rows*
